title: (x) 50 years at ringside - (similar to) Koch Original, Stymie {Marten Fischer}
content:
does anyone know what this typeface is .. or something close to it ?  
it looks like Kabel but i couldn't find the "5"

thanks in advance

 ![](http://web.archive.org/web/20140719203155im_/http:/typophile.com/files/50_6705.jpg)
author: serviceforthepeople

comments.content: ...and "50" could be an expanded [Rockwell](http://web.archive.org/web/20140719203155/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/rockwell-mt-2/)? Or maybe some version of [Stymie](http://web.archive.org/web/20140719203155/http:/www.myfonts.com/search?search%5Btext%5D=Stymie)?
thanks marten. i think its from the 70s.
Could be film type that doesn't exist digitally.
i was suspecting that ... thanks anyways .. i think i can get pretty close with stymie and koch.
